('96427','33261','5','Unique luxury villa with panoramic views in the southwest of Mallorca'),
('96428','33262','5','In a unique location, overlooking the south west coast of Majorca,  from Portals Nous to Palma Nova, this Villa was built in the 90ies with high quality materials. This estate can accommodate up to 14 people. Over the entrance on the ground floor you  enter a large entrance hall witha big reception salon. At this level there are a wardrobe,a guest toilet, an office, laundry room, exercise room, lounge with fireplace (approx 70sqm), spacious living room with open kitchen, pantry, 2. guest toilet and walk-in cold room. On the 1st floor are the master bedroom with 2 dressing rooms, a bathroom and a terrace. Here are also 6 guest bedrooms (5 with en-suite bathrooms). The secluded garden area, with its open and covered terraces and a large pool invites to celebrate or relax. In the pool house there is a washmachine room and a bathroom with toilet and shower. The high-quality facilities includes among others a lift, underfloor heating (oil / water), air-conditioning w / c and double glazed wooden windows. 3 cars can be parked under a carport or on other open parking spaces. The villa is in excellent condition and is also suitable for all year-round occupancy'),
